Changelog
=========

This document describes changes between each past release. For information
about future releases, check `milestones`_.


0.4 (unreleased)
----------------

Enhance development environment.

- Feature #3 - Development environment now uses Tox (was using zc.buildout).
  Tox runs the tests. TravisCI.org runs Tox.


0.3 (2013-10-14)
----------------

- Fixed "'package' must be a string" error when installing project.


0.2 (2013-10-11)
----------------

- Fixed upload on PyPI.


0.1 (2013-10-11)
----------------

- Imported PlainPasswordHasher implementation by Boris Feld.


